[I] The Code Object Manager

[T] The Code Object Manager is a library which provides operations for
[T] creating and inspecting LLVM code objects.

[U] https://github.com/ROCm/llvm-project/

[A] Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[F] CROSS OBJDIR
